Step 7 — Control interface
A single pygame window combining everything: the GPS map with all bikes and event zones colored by confidence, a camera feed panel (switchable between bikes by clicking their triangle on the map), buttons for spawn obstacle / remove obstacle / spawn new bike. This is the demo-ready deliverable.

Step 8 — Single launch file
One command starts everything: CARLA is already external, but one ros2 launch brings up all nodes, all bikes, the interface. Optional arguments: number of bikes, obstacle count, map name.
